reviews_data.review_text: We moved around the corner from this place about 18 months ago and every time I drive past I kick myself for not remembering to go for breakfast. Well we finally went and I'm so glad I did. This place is cute, the staff is friendly, and our food was delicious. My wife and I both got the sausage egg and cheese on a croissant. I'm about halfway through mine and was moved to write this review. So happy we went, we will be back!
Everything I've had here has been super delicious and authentic. They are also very kind which always makes it a pleasure to stop in and grab my favorites :)
Love this place! The staff is friendly and most everything there is good - my favorites are the spinach pie, dolmades, and their espresso.
Love this place!  All the Greek food and pastries are just delicious!  I'm a regular there--I must get a spanakopita there weekly! Ever try their hot dogs? They're fantastic, too.
Everything is delicious and the neighborhood is enticing too.

The breakfast sandwiches here are unmatched! The value and taste are on point. You need to try them out. The coffee is unbeatable too - do yourself a favor and try the mochacchino!  Friendliest employees ever too!

Coming from NYC and knowing that we could find a big Greek community, we anticipated to find a Greek pastry shop cafeteria style where we could enjoy a frappe coffee and taste so many pastries and cookies ..We then visited MOCCO Bistro ..a hop away from the center of uptown...this place is a paradise outside of Greece...everything is baked in premises by the best Baker Haido, is basing all her baking on traditional and authentic grand mother mother's old recipes..wether she makes the big triangle of phyllo filled with feta bechamel , or her famous spinach feta pie . Baklava, galaktoboureko, big chocolate or staberry cakes, koulourakia cookies and too many to list them...A .quick salad with a cheese pie triangle, accompanied by an aromatic tea, the betb choice for a quick bite! Do not miss this place...add it immediately at your " must to do list!!
